        <section>
            <h1>2. AI-Based Predictive Maintenance for Manufacturing</h1>
            <p>
                This system predicts **equipment failures in manufacturing plants** using sensor data and AI algorithms.  
                It detects **patterns of wear and tear** in machinery and **alerts operators before a breakdown occurs**.  
                The goal is to **reduce downtime and maintenance costs**.
            </p>
            <h3>Technology Used:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Python & TensorFlow</li>
                <li>Time-Series Analysis</li>
                <li>IoT Edge Devices</li>
                <li>Predictive Analytics Algorithms</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
